  "text": "Spacetime emerges as we integrate out the off diagonal part. When x + → −∞, we reach the singularity in sugra, and a week coupling super Yang-Mills theory in matrix. As argued by [CITATION_1] , simply integrating out is not allowed. We must deal with the whole non-Abelian degrees of freedom. To us, there is no sign of breakdown of matrix theory. More rigorous matrix calculation is needed to say anything more.",
